Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley in town. My name is Sarah. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah, I'm having a bit of trouble with my recent bill.

I'm sorry to hear that! I'll do my best to help you. May I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Michael Anderson.

Thank you, Michael. Could you please provide me with your account number?

Certainly, my account number is one two three four five six.

Great! And can you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number for verification, please?

Yes, the last four digits are seven eight nine zero.

Thank you for that information, Michael. I see the issue with the billing now. It appears there was an error with the charge calculation. I'll correct it and send you an updated statement.

I appreciate that, Sarah. Thank you for your help.

You're welcome, Michael. Thank you for your patience and for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
